      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> tomato paste</strong> in 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]<strong> </span>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped sun-dried tomatoes</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>dried oregano </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1661184260722-x200.jpg",
