            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your<strong> cannellini beans</strong> then add them to the pan with your <strong>finely</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>,<strong> tomato stock</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, reduce the heat to low-medium and cook, covered for 10 min or until the <strong>bean</strong> <strong>stew</strong> has thickened slightly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1661184265314-x200.jpg",
